like":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你啦仲話香港貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係美國用緊verizon每個月交緊80美金</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美國人搵幾錢一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美國2016 年平均人工一年 $44148. 人工扣除一俾人工既30% 稅, 實則每個月約 $20000 港幣月薪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thebalance.com/average-salary-information-for-us-workers-2060808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebalance.com%2Faverage-salary-information-for-us-workers-2060808&d=49yC84XGkIvLbS4T9B%2FwoP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=cffc0d3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thebalance.com/average-salary-information-for-us-workers-2060808</a><br />\n<br />\n香港2016 年平均月收入$15451, 扣除稅一年要俾約$1100 蚊, 實側每個月落袋 $15360<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tradingeconomics.com/hong-kong/wages\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftradingeconomics.com%2Fhong-kong%2Fwages&d=49yC84XGkIvLbS4T9B%2FwoP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ba83528e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tradingeconomics.com/hong-kong/wages</a><br />\n<br />\n即係美國人工高香港average 30%.  上面個人俾緊80美金一個月, 30% off 的話等於要俾$435 港幣電話上網.<br />\n<br />\n我估你香港大部份簽2年約都未洗俾400幾蚊電話費. 你要講慘你望左大陸大城市收入好似上海, 再睇佢地電話手機費先再呻香港貴"},{"pid":"033c886c9ea4a8d65299efd99b1a7f4c7226a2b2","tid":342251,"uid":86699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"香港上網真係平，而且網速唔差（除咗喺繁忙時間搭地鐵）<br />\n加拿大上網就真係貴！ 而且又唔係收得好（喊出嚟）"}]}